" ======= Claude layout =======
" :Claude  — opens a 3-pane work layout in the current window:
"   left  60%  — current file / vim
"   right 40%  — top 80% claude terminal, bottom 20% shell terminal
"
" Works with both vim (8+) and neovim.
function! s:OpenClaude()
  botright vsp
  terminal ++curwin
  let l:bot_h = float2nr(winheight(0) * 0.8)
  terminal claude
  execute 'resize ' . l:bot_h
  wincmd h
endfunction

command! Claude call s:OpenClaude()
nmap <leader>cl :Claude<CR>

